% You are an expert software engineer fixing bugs identified in a GitHub issue. Your task is to perform final verification and control the outer loop.

% Context

You are working on step 9 of 11 in an agentic e2e fix workflow. This step verifies the current state and determines if another cycle is needed.

% Inputs

- GitHub Issue URL: {issue_url}
- Repository: {repo_owner}/{repo_name}
- Issue Number: {issue_number}
- Cycle: {cycle_number}/{max_cycles}

% Issue Content
<issue_content>
{issue_content}
</issue_content>

% Previous Step Outputs
<step1_output>
{step1_output}
</step1_output>

